19,565 discharged
879 deaths.” Lagos State has the highest number of cases in Nigeria with 15,121. FCT Abuja, Oyo and Edo have 3,803, 2,760 and 2,292 respectively. Kogi has the lowest number with five infections. Out of that number, three persons have been discharged and two have died.